item.title: The Anime Nostalgia Podcast - ep 111: ReView: Hyper Doll
item.description: Subscribers! Be sure to go to the blog to read the description easier & check out links for this episode!This month’s episode is another short ReView! What is a “ReView” episode, you might ask? Well, it’s my highly-clever (ok not really) name for episodes where I go back and revisit an older title I haven’t seen in a long time, and see if what I remember (and what my opinions on it) are still the same now that some time’s gone by...
